hoejhus_remix by Lickwim

This remix of hoejhus features some new iteresting and fun content/additions.

- Custom Textures: Entire map is made from custom textures that I created myself, there is no default textures from the editor at all.

- Sounds: Some nice/funny startup sounds and some special gameplay sounds in the map. (from mario kart: 64)

- Level Improvements: Fixed all sorts of bugs/leaks from the old map.

- Level Addition: New funny skybox with a spinning sun at the bottom of the map, a jail that players will get teleported into instead of just dying when they fall out of the map and a bridge with some platforms under the map that hosts a small addition/secret.

Also, credits to the guy who created the first map, who apparently nobody knows of..
